message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero
